OL,3,CExpansion of major road could be
OL,4,Cscrapped following government
OL,5,Cannouncement
OL,7,FThe project to upgrade the A38 in
OL,8,FDerby could be scrapped following
OL,9,Fgovernment plans to cut funding for
OL,10,Froad projects.
OL,12,FEarlier this year the Government
OL,13,Fcommitted to fund upgrades to the busy
OL,14,Froad.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
