FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782892079
OL,3,CExpansion of major road could be
OL,4,Cscrapped following government
OL,5,Cannouncement
OL,7,FWork would involve the creation of
OL,8,Fflyovers, underpasses, and roads
OL,9,Fwidened from four lanes (two on either
OL,10,Fside) to six (three on either side) to
OL,11,Fease congestion on one of the city's
OL,12,Fbusiest routes. It was reported the
OL,13,Fproject could cost around #600m.
OL,15,FBut in a new statement the Mayor of
OL,16,Fthe East Midlands Claire Ward
OL,17,Fsuggested the scheme may now not go
OL,18,Fahead ` calling it "completely
OL,19,Funacceptable".
OL,26,@zD@TOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782892079
OL,3,CExpansion of major road could be
OL,4,Cscrapped following government
OL,5,Cannouncement
OL,7,FIt follows Tuesday's (June 30)
OL,8,Fspending announcements made by Prime
OL,9,FMinister Keir Starmer on the Defence
OL,10,FInvestment Plan ` which is reported to
OL,11,Fsee an additional #15 billion for the
OL,12,Farmed forces. A #60 billion spend is
OL,13,Fplanned on defence over the next four
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,FBut the Prime Minister warned that
OL,17,Fsome capital projects, such as roads
OL,18,Fand energy investment ,"will no longer
OL,19,Fgo ahead as planned".
OL,26,@zD@XO]{D@TO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782892079
OL,3,CExpansion of major road could be
OL,4,Cscrapped following government
OL,5,Cannouncement
OL,7,FThe A38 was not specifically mentioned
OL,8,Fin the PM's speech. He said this was
OL,9,F"about taking the necessary choices `
OL,10,Fthe right choices to protect our
OL,11,Fnation".
OL,13,FBut Ms Ward, Mayor of the East
OL,14,FMidlands Combined County Authority
OL,15,F(EMCCA), has said in a statement the
OL,16,FA38 project could be under serious
OL,17,Fdoubt as well as improvements to the
OL,18,FA46 Newark Bypass in Nottinghamshire.
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782892079
OL,3,CExpansion of major road could be
OL,4,Cscrapped following government
OL,5,Cannouncement
OL,7,FHer critical statement claimed the
OL,8,FEast Midlands could lose out on
OL,9,Fhundreds of millions of pounds of
OL,10,Finvestment.
OL,12,FShe said: "The proposal to remove
OL,13,Finvestment from two road schemes in
OL,14,Fthe East Midlands ` into the A46 and
OL,15,FA38 - is completely unacceptable to me.
OL,26,@tD@KOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782892079
OL,3,CExpansion of major road could be
OL,4,Cscrapped following government
OL,5,Cannouncement
OL,7,F"I was informed of this decision as
OL,8,Fthe Prime Minister was delivering his
OL,9,Fspeech on the Defence Investment Plan.
OL,10,FIf Mayors and their regions are to be
OL,11,Fseen as respected partners of
OL,12,Fgovernment, we need to be treated like
OL,13,Fgrown-ups and involved in trade-offs
OL,14,Fwhich affect our regions.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782892079
OL,3,CExpansion of major road could be
OL,4,Cscrapped following government
OL,5,Cannouncement
OL,7,F"The trade-offs here are ones I
OL,8,Funderstand. I understand that
OL,9,Fincreasing investment into defence
OL,10,Fmeans removing it from other things. I
OL,11,Funderstand that everywhere will need
OL,12,Fto contribute so that we can be safe
OL,13,Fin a less certain world.
OL,15,F"What I cannot understand is why the
OL,16,Fonly region being asked to lose #900
OL,17,Fmillion of investment into its roads
OL,18,Fis the East Midlands ` that is not
OL,19,Fequitable and fails to recognise the
OL,20,Fdecades of underinvestment that have
OL,21,Fpreceded today's decision.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782892079
OL,3,CExpansion of major road could be
OL,4,Cscrapped following government
OL,5,Cannouncement
OL,7,F"The East Midlands will play its part
OL,8,Fin delivering a safer world ` we have
OL,9,Fstrengths in defence and will be
OL,10,Finvesting into those alongside the
OL,11,Fgovernment.
OL,13,F"But people working in defence need
OL,14,Fgood roads so that their staff can get
OL,15,Fto work, access their supply chains,
OL,16,Fand trade. We will not serve our
OL,17,Fdefence sector well if we under invest
OL,18,Finto its enabling infrastructure.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782892079
OL,3,CExpansion of major road could be
OL,4,Cscrapped following government
OL,5,Cannouncement
OL,7,F"The Government must seek
OL,8,Fcontributions from regions other than
OL,9,Fours and from spending areas other
OL,10,Fthan roads. This is what I am asking
OL,11,FMinisters for today."
OL,13,FIn a statement the Treasury said:
OL,14,F"This (defence) package has been
OL,15,Ffunded by reprioritising public
OL,16,Fspending, acting within our fiscal
OL,17,Frules and without taking resources
OL,18,Faway from day-to-day spending on
OL,19,Ffrontline services.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@UO]vD@AOUvD@GpmvD@Opn
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,343,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F342A1782892079
OL,3,CExpansion of major road could be
OL,4,Cscrapped following government
OL,5,Cannouncement
OL,7,F"It is funded primarily by
OL,8,Freallocating budget from across
OL,9,Fgovernment departments, with #10.3
OL,10,Fbillion identified now. A further #4.7
OL,11,Fbillion over four years will be
OL,12,Fconfirmed at Budget 2026, in a fair
OL,13,Fand balanced way.
OL,15,F"We will ensure that we focus this on
OL,16,Ffinding efficiencies, cancelling or
OL,17,Fdelaying lower priority programmes and
OL,18,Fremaining ruthlessly focussed on value
OL,19,Ffor money for the taxpayer."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/10
